{"tid":2405635,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當年雙非問題，支共曾經恐嚇香港人，香港永久居民身份係無可取消","createTime":"2021-02-12T13:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T14:52:28.000Z","uid":301952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3532961d8dbd464f4b50eb0ae977d0b5769f54d0","tid":2405635,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=99ETA8w8rjs&amp;list=PLuwJy35eAVaICMi7K4nEmiCm7VgWJZ93N&amp;index=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D99ETA8w8rjs%26list%3DPLuwJy35eAVaICMi7K4nEmiCm7VgWJZ93N%26index%3D11&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FFLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=9d548653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=99ETA8w8rjs&amp;list=PLuwJy35eAVaICMi7K4nEmiCm7VgWJZ93N&amp;index=11</a><br />\n38:28<br />\n<br />\n當年支共逼香港人硬啃雙非，話雙非得到左既香港永久身分證係冇辦法取消<br />\n因為鄧小平當年都驚繼任人，向香港人開刀鵲巢鳩占<br />\n所以一國兩制設計到永久居港權係冇方法取消<br />\n雙非在法律上都被「帶脅」，所以後悔黎左生仔既一樣取消唔到居港權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae8ae6bbc11bf3abf606b6dd0353b3033c72bbd","tid":2405635,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iTV8jK8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTV8jK8.gif&h=5a110c00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2244032c06d25c66ad5617f431da40163b7f7f","tid":2405635,"uid":301952